org.sbml.jsbml.math.compiler

Interface AbstractASTNodeCompiler


  • public interface AbstractASTNodeCompiler
    A compiler for abstract syntax trees. This compiler evaluates the values represented by ASTNode2s. It defines how to perform mathematical or other operations on these data types. Recursion can be performed as follows: 
       public ASTNodeValue doSomeThing(AbstractASTNode ast) {
     ...
     ASTNodeValue child = ast.compile(this);
     ...
     return new ASTNodeValue(doSomeThing(child), this);
   }
